<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="slide-v">slide <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /slaɪd/    美 /slaɪd/  </p>
<p>(slid, slid)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(使) 滑行；(使) 滑动：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I saw a man sliding on a banana skin.
我看到有个人踩在香蕉皮上滑了一下。</p><footer>人教④ – 3</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>滑落：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The pen slid from his hand.
笔从他手中滑落下来。</p></div>

<h4 id="3-slip">3.★ <strong>(使) 悄悄移到；(使) 悄悄移动(slip)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>slide into</strong> a room
偷偷地溜进房间</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>slide sth into</strong> a drawer
把某物偷偷塞进抽屉</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.<strong>逐渐败坏；开始出现问题：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>slide into</strong> bad habits
不知不觉地沾染上坏习惯</p></div></div>